{"tid":629194,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺好多人懶尻識食, 講到香港一蘭同日本爭九皮","createTime":"2018-04-14T13:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T13:41:14.000Z","uid":22839,"like":82,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c259c6cf9fd2c7e00116e81458bc78e693d22878","tid":629194,"uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:16:32.000Z","msg":"你可以覺得一蘭唔算好食<br />\n但講到日本一蘭好食過香港真係得啖笑<br />\n日本香港兩邊我各食過10次以上<br />\n我肯定根本唔會有大分別<br />\n但好多港人剩係食過一次半次日本一蘭<br />\n就當自己係拉面達人<br />\n係都要踩香港版一蘭扲存在感<br />\n<br />\np.s. 當然價錢上香港比起日本一定係唔抵食"},{"pid":"3f03dd837d30793b2b28d79c1e7e68f67126eb72","tid":629194,"uid":140666,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T14:39:49.000Z","msg":"成日都有架啦<br />\n例如 你話 我覺得xxx 幾好食喎<br />\n之後就有人話 吓 我覺得xxx 好普通 yyy 好好多囉"},{"pid":"7499e7d112b2a072083fabff633d14922f0675d2","tid":629194,"uid":129506,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T14:53:24.000Z","msg":"心理因素，話比人知日本食同香港食一樣味咪即係話自己on9<br />\n<br />\n梗係要話日本好食啲，令自己與眾不同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8862abea154d4719950bfdca5877ec8daff4ebd4","tid":629194,"uid":85132,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T15:11:50.000Z","msg":"個問題係香港冇餸呀， 加餸逐樣計錢"},{"pid":"85fc850f2c9590f70495e6cad5c8f0c88a227b31","tid":629194,"uid":11474,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T15:16:15.000Z","msg":"其實好似香港真係淡味少少 但分別唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bddf704c3f1dccfd8dcb13fdbe957d8385accf7","tid":629194,"uid":815,"like":12,"dislike":16,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T22:23:46.000Z","msg":"崇日撚連出前一丁都話日版好食啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明就一鳩樣味"},{"pid":"3870884e41688131b0c44f340b38a34a67c2bb8e","tid":629194,"uid":6058,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"9bddf704c3f1dccfd8dcb13fdbe957d8385accf7","tid":629194,"uid":815,"like":12,"dislike":16,